==[[Hindi]]==
===Interrogative pronoun===
'''क्या''' (kyā)

# [[what]]

===Interrogative particle===
'''क्या''' (kyā)

# initial interrogative particle. In this usage, it does not have a direct translation as a word in English, it simply makes a statement into a question.
#:Example: क्या आप यहाँ रहते हैं? (kyā āp yahā̃ rehte haĩ?) "Do you live here?

====Translations====
*Chinese: [[嗎]], [[吗]] (ma, final rather than initial)
*Japanese: [[か]] (ka, final rather than initial)
*[[Khmer]]: [[េទ]] (final rather than initial)
*Mongolian: [[уу]] (uu), [[үү]] (üü), [[юуу]] (yuu), [[юүү]] (yüü)
*Thai: [[ไหม]] (mãi, final rather than initial)
*[[Urdu]]: [[كيا]]
*German: [[Was]]